extendedInfo.description: * A dual-core device is recommended, but try it out anyways :) *MUST! CHOP! is the slicing game for pros. Your job is to cut fruit & veggies into a number of slices, before the time runs out. Whether it's to slice an apple into 2 pieces, or 5 pineapples into 15, this game will test your speed, coordination and quick thinking (or counting).But hopefully, you'll have fun playing it :)Keywords: fruit, slicing, ninja, chop, slice, coolness beyond belief, best game evar, completely humble, etc
